                        "expectedResult": "<p>Sign in button must be clickable.</p>\n",
                        "notes": ""
                    },
                    {
                        "action": "<p>Enter invalid email and a random password, then correct email.</p>\n",
                        "expectedResult": "<p>1-) Signin should not be clickable in the first action</p>\n\n<p>2-) Signin should be clickable after correction</p>\n",
