                    {
                        "action": "<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">AC 6. c</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha; margin-bottom:11px\">\n\t<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">User must be able to save or cancel when he <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/00a7RS7nHjuSl5CCA4n3w4/Settings?node-id=238-16207&amp;t=2RwJT5wssf9oXc0n-4\">switches the system default toogle to OFF</a> <strong>and </strong>makes a change in any setting field.</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">\n\t<li style=\"margin-left:78px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Toggle off changes are saved or not saved functionality</span></span></span></li>\n\t<li style=\"margin-left:78px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Should be able to make changes in any setting field.</span></span></span></li>\n\t<li style=\"margin-left:78px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Keep editing should show the changed settings.</span></span></span></li>\n\t<li style=\"margin-left:78px; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Discard changes should reset the previous selection and Save, Cancel button disabled.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Test Steps:</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Login to Toolbox</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Settings</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Toggle Off</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Edit Language, Temperature, Distance, Time and Format</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Cancel button</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Unsaved Change dialog box should appear</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Clicking on Keep editing should bring back to Settings screen with the selection and also Save and Cancel button enabled</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Clicking on discard changes should show the previous selection and save and cancel button disabled to its original state</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Save button after editing the fields</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif\">Verify Changes successfully saved message with save and cancel button getting disabled.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n",
                        "expectedResult": "<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/00a7RS7nHjuSl5CCA4n3w4/Settings?node-id=238-16207&amp;t=2RwJT5wssf9oXc0n-4\">switches the system default toogle to OFF</a></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif\">Verify Changes successfully saved message with save and cancel button getting disabled.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Cancel Button dialog box</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"222\" src=\"https://porscheebike.jamacloud.com/attachment/2581/image-L559rHALJD.png\" width=\"527\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Changes Saved</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"334\" src=\"https://porscheebike.jamacloud.com/attachment/2582/image-13LNXOLIRT.png\" width=\"527\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
                        "notes": ""
                    },
                    {
                        "action": "<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">AC 6. d</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha; margin-bottom:11px\">\n\t<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Application must revert the default settings when<a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/00a7RS7nHjuSl5CCA4n3w4/Settings?node-id=238-16135&amp;t=M3BD183tpVgUuNHh-4\"> system default toogle</a> <strong>switched </strong>to ON although there are unsaved settings.</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">\n\t<li style=\"margin-left:55px; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">System to set PC default settings when the Toggle is On always though if there are any unsaved settings.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Test Steps:</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Login to Toolbox</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Settings</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Toggle On</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Verify the PC default settings</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n",
                        "expectedResult": "<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/00a7RS7nHjuSl5CCA4n3w4/Settings?node-id=238-16135&amp;t=M3BD183tpVgUuNHh-4\">system default toogle</a></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Verify PC </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">default settings of different language screen shot here.</span></span></span></p>\n",
                        "notes": ""
                    },
                    {
                        "action": "<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">AC 6. e</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha; margin-bottom:11px\">\n\t<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:8px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">User must be able to change screens when toogle is OFF but no change is done.</span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">\n\t<li style=\"margin-left:55px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Toggle off and change/edit the settings to which ever user want it and save the settings.</span></span></span></li>\n\t<li style=\"margin-left:55px; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">User should be move around to other pages in the Toolbox</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Test Steps:</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Login to Toolbox</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Settings</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Toggle off</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Edit settings with different selections</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><spa