                    {
                        "action": "<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">AC 6. i</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha; margin-bottom:11px\">\n\t<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:8px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Application must show that toogle is ON and defaults are set when user returns back to settings.</span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">\n\t<li style=\"margin-left:56px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Toggle off and change/edit the settings, save, move around to different pages performance other actions.</span></span></span></li>\n\t<li style=\"margin-left:56px; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">User should be able to see defaults settings when returns back to the default settings.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Test Steps:</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Login to Toolbox</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Settings</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Toggle off</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Edit settings with different selections</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Save</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on System Overview</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Settings</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Select Toggle On</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">User should be able to see PC defaults settings when returns back to the settings page.</span></span></span></p>\n",
                        "expectedResult": "<p>Verify U<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">ser should be able to see defaults settings when returns back to the default settings.</span></span></span></p>\n",
                        "notes": ""
                    },
                    {
                        "action": "<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><strong>AC 7</strong> User must have English language as set on initial launch if the user system language is not defined in the application.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">\n\t<li style=\"margin-left:56px; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">English language selection to be made when the PC settings language is not defined within the application. Example: Chinese, Syria etc.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Test Steps:</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Select system Settings</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Time and language</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Language and region</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Login to Toolbox</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Click on Settings</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Verify the English language selection is made.</span></span></span></p>\n",
                        "expectedResult": "<p>Verify&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">English language selection to be made when the PC settings language is not defined within the application.</span></span></span></p>\n",
                        "notes": ""
