                        "notes": "<p><strong>Note:</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>1. The correctness of the error message will be checked in future stories.</p>\n\n<p><strong>2.</strong> This story is only for the view error messages on firmwae update fialure but the verifying each error messages correctness will be part of turture stories</p>\n\n<p><strong>3.</strong>&nbsp;Source of Error Code Table ---&gt; <a href=\"https://porsche-ep.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SD/pages/2583560205/31XXXX+Ride60+Firmware+Update+Process\">31XXXX Ride60 Firmware Update Process</a>&nbsp;is pulled to generate \"error messages\"</p>\n\n<p><strong>Error Section Columns includes:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Severity, Code, Products,Description and Cause, Solution</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n"
                    },
                    {
                        "action": "<p>Click on the \"Icon\" to Check error messages can be expanded and collapsed</p>\n\n<p>For both single errors and multiple errors</p>\n",
                        "expectedResult": "<p>User must be also able to <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/nWRkR2TADpL6ZlNuTKgcnu/Firmware-update?node-id=6727-44814&amp;t=pn2BwqTo86InDWYZ-4\">expand multiple errors </a>at the same time</p>\n",
                        "notes": ""
                    },
                    {
                        "action": "<p>Click on Expand</p>\n",
                        "expectedResult": "<p>User must be able to see <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/nWRkR2TADpL6ZlNuTKgcnu/Firmware-update?node-id=6727-44717&amp;t=pn2BwqTo86InDWYZ-4\">cause and solution</a> if expend the error</p>\n",
                        "notes": ""
                    },
                    {
                        "action": "<p>Check their is no quick fix section</p>\n",
                        "expectedResult": "<p>User <strong>must not</strong> view the general quick fixes section</p>\n",
                        "notes": ""
                    },
                    {
                        "action": "<p>Follow the test steps 1 to 11</p>\n\n<p>Disconnect \"USB\" from the bike set up after 20% update</p>\n",
                        "expectedResult": "<p>User must be able to disconnect USB after 20% update</p>\n",
                        "notes": "<p><strong>Note: </strong>All scenarios from Error code Table cannot be checked due to the testing and hardware dependency, will need to be taken up in future stories.</p>\n"
                    }
